bt was too large to salvage the existing system, and that a full rebuild was necessary. With mentorship from the Sr. Technical Architect, I redesigned the database to normalize the data. The original data was migrated into the new structure which resulted in an 85% reduction in size without any impact on data integrity. The new normalized database enabled us to write efficient code that significantly improved the system performance.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.beadonor.ca/\">Visit Site</a></p>'),(3410,289,'_summary_body','field_5a4ab43dee001'),(3411,289,'summary_list_0_name','Laravel'),(3412,289,'_summary_list_0_name','field_5a4ab477ee003'),(3413,289,'summary_list_1_name','PHP'),(3414,289,'_summary_list_1_name','field_5a4ab477ee003'),(3415,289,'summary_list_2_name','SQL'),(3416,289,'_summary_list_2_name','field_5a4ab477ee003'),(3417,289,'summary_list_3_name','Relational Database Design'),(3418,289,'_summary_list_3_name','field_5a4ab477ee003'),(3419,289,'summary_list','6'),(3420,289,'_summary_list','field_5a4ab453ee002'),(3421,289,'summary',''),(3422,289,'_summary','field_5a4ab407edfff'),(3423,289,'media_type','gallery'),(3424,289,'_media_type','field_5acaaf2e198c9'),(3425,289,'gallery_0_image','290'),(3426,289,'_gallery_0_image','field_5a4ab3a6ce284'),(3427,289,'gallery_1_image','291'),(3428,289,'_gallery_1_image','field_5a4ab3a6ce284'),(3429,289,'gallery_2_image','292'),(3430,289,'_gallery_2_image','field_5a4ab3a6ce284'),(3431,289,'gallery','3'),(3432,289,'_gallery','field_5a4ab373ce283'),(3433,289,'project_type','a:1:{i:0;s:1:\"8\";}'),(3434,289,'_project_type','field_5acc188943b6e'),(3435,289,'summary_list_4_name','Data Normalization'),(3436,289,'_summary_list_4_name','field_5a4ab477ee003'),(3437,293,'_edit_last','1'),(3438,293,'_edit_lock','1524456383:1'),(3439,294,'_wp_attached_file','2018/04/1direction_large_01.jpg'),(3440,294,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:814;s:6:\"height\";i:462;s:4:\"file\";s:31:\"2018/04/1dir